SUMMARY:Commander Night @ Queen & Rook Game Tavern! @ Queen and Rook Game 
 Cafe
LOCATION:Queen and Rook Game Cafe\, 117A South Street\, Philadelphia\, Pen
 nsylvania\, 19106
DESCRIPTION:Format: Commander\nCost: Free\nStore: https://queenandrookcafe
 .com/\nDetails: https://locator.wizards.com/events/10518585\n\nJoin us eve
 ry Wednesday for what many players hail as "The Best Commander Night on th
 e East Coast!" Attendance is typically in the 50-60 range\, with turnouts 
 sometimes as high as 70! There's NO entry fee\, & NO assigned seating (but
  plz consider getting something to eat/drink so we can stay alive <3)\n\nW
 e have a wide range of players both new & old\, as well as regular cEDH po
 ds if you've been looking to try it out. \n\nJoin us on our Discord at htt
 p://bit.ly/QNRDC for more info & to connect with the wider Philadelphia Ga
 ming Community!\nSource: wizards-locator
URL;VALUE=URI:https://locator.wizards.com/events/10518585
END:VEVENT
